metadata.name: Space Time
metadata.description:
This clock weaves a tapestry of time that dictates the very course of the universe, encompassing the past, present and future all at once. It has a wisdom and intelligence that surpasses moral comprehension.

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. Featuring 100 AI artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
